WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 16=

00:00:06.380 --> 00:00:07.700
Zhu Lingtai!

00:00:07.780 --> 00:00:09.420
How dare you all!

00:00:09.700 --> 00:00:11.540
You actually used
a fake deer to deceive me!

00:00:11.820 --> 00:00:14.140
Someone! Investigate this thoroughly!

00:00:14.580 --> 00:00:15.579
Consort Shu.

00:00:15.580 --> 00:00:16.500
Crown Prince.

00:00:16.580 --> 00:00:17.900
You are confined for one month

00:00:18.860 --> 00:00:20.300
and forbidden from leaving the palace.

00:00:21.100 --> 00:00:22.699
Grandfather, don't be upset.

00:00:22.700 --> 00:00:26.100
I'm the greatest blessing
Heaven has given you.

00:00:40.220 --> 00:00:42.099
(Longevity)
This is the character for longevity!

00:00:42.100 --> 00:00:44.180
Amazing.

00:00:44.780 --> 00:00:46.860
This is incredible.

00:00:49.460 --> 00:00:50.740
Ah!

00:00:51.060 --> 00:00:52.859
You're hurting me to death!

00:00:52.860 --> 00:00:55.299
Your Highness, I know my mistake.

00:00:55.300 --> 00:00:56.020
Get out!

00:00:56.220 --> 00:00:57.220
Yes.

00:01:10.220 --> 00:01:12.260
Didn't I tell you to get out?

00:01:12.780 --> 00:01:14.019
Are you satisfied

00:01:14.020 --> 00:01:15.860
with my massage skills?

00:01:21.380 --> 00:01:22.700
You.

00:01:22.780 --> 00:01:24.500
So you still remembered to come back.

00:01:24.820 --> 00:01:26.299
While you were away,

00:01:26.300 --> 00:01:27.379
your subordinates

00:01:27.380 --> 00:01:29.260
couldn't even handle a little girl.

00:01:29.460 --> 00:01:30.739
In all these years,

00:01:30.740 --> 00:01:32.580
I've never been this humiliated.

00:01:32.700 --> 00:01:35.140
Hahaha.

00:01:35.580 --> 00:01:36.820
Your Highness.

00:01:37.340 --> 00:01:38.859
Don't worry, Your Highness.

00:01:38.860 --> 00:01:41.300
I already have a foolproof plan.

00:01:41.380 --> 00:01:44.100
The people who offended you today

00:01:44.300 --> 00:01:46.500
will definitely pay the price.

00:01:58.340 --> 00:01:59.339
Prince Jing.

00:01:59.340 --> 00:02:01.620
You really found yourself a treasure.

00:02:01.780 --> 00:02:04.179
Ever since Suisui entered the palace,

00:02:04.180 --> 00:02:06.579
my back and legs don't ache anymore,

00:02:06.580 --> 00:02:09.979
and even my spirits
have improved greatly.

00:02:09.980 --> 00:02:11.060
Of course.

00:02:11.180 --> 00:02:12.359
(Memorial)
You even let Suisui

00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:13.579
read memorials with me.

00:02:13.580 --> 00:02:15.060
How could you not feel better?

00:02:18.720 --> 00:02:23.120
(Reduce taxes for disaster victims)

00:02:24.500 --> 00:02:26.179
Grandfather, this one is good.

00:02:26.180 --> 00:02:27.179
It's shiny and golden.

00:02:27.180 --> 00:02:28.300
Hmm.

00:02:34.860 --> 00:02:35.699
Hmm.

00:02:35.700 --> 00:02:37.020
A good memorial indeed.

00:02:37.580 --> 00:02:40.100
This one proposes
reducing taxes for disaster victims.

00:02:42.580 --> 00:02:43.700
Hmm.

00:02:43.780 --> 00:02:46.620
Grandfather, what's this?

00:02:46.700 --> 00:02:49.699
This is called the Imperial Seal.

00:02:49.700 --> 00:02:51.100
It's used for stamping.

00:02:51.260 --> 00:02:53.059
Whoever stamps something with it,

00:02:53.060 --> 00:02:54.819
that thing belongs to them.

00:02:54.820 --> 00:02:56.980
Hahaha.

00:02:58.700 --> 00:02:59.379
Hey.

00:02:59.380 --> 00:03:00.179
Suisui.

00:03:00.180 --> 00:03:01.179
Don't be rude.

00:03:01.180 --> 00:03:03.340
Hahaha.

00:03:03.900 --> 00:03:05.739
I like Grandfather the most.

00:03:05.740 --> 00:03:07.499
Now that I stamped it,

00:03:07.500 --> 00:03:10.499
does that mean
Grandfather belongs to me now?

00:03:10.500 --> 00:03:12.499
And all of Grandfather's treasures

00:03:12.500 --> 00:03:14.099
belong to me too?

00:03:14.100 --> 00:03:15.500
Hahaha.

00:03:15.780 --> 00:03:18.900
(This girl really has Father
wrapped around her finger.)

00:03:21.260 --> 00:03:23.659
Your Majesty. Your Highness.
Something terrible has happened.

00:03:23.660 --> 00:03:26.020
A fire broke out
at the grain depot in Jiacheng Pass.

00:03:26.220 --> 00:03:28.979
The soldiers tried their best,
but less than ten percent was saved.

00:03:28.980 --> 00:03:29.980
What?

00:03:30.060 --> 00:03:30.979
Not only that,

00:03:30.980 --> 00:03:34.899
rumors are spreading among the people
that the recent disasters happened because...

00:03:34.900 --> 00:03:36.579
Because of what? Speak!

00:03:36.580 --> 00:03:38.200
Because an evil girl
has entered the court.

00:03:38.200 --> 00:03:39.580
His Majesty dotes on the evil girl

00:03:39.620 --> 00:03:41.640
and the prince cursed
with the lone star of misfortune,

00:03:41.860 --> 00:03:43.380
thus angering the heavens.

00:03:44.180 --> 00:03:45.540
Ridiculous!

00:03:45.700 --> 00:03:46.859
Pass on my decree.

00:03:46.860 --> 00:03:47.459
Investigate

00:03:47.460 --> 00:03:48.820
these rumors thoroughly.

00:03:48.980 --> 00:03:50.859
Whoever dares spread rumors again

00:03:50.860 --> 00:03:52.300
will be beaten to death!

00:03:52.460 --> 00:03:54.019
I want to see

00:03:54.020 --> 00:03:55.859
whether their tongues are tougher

00:03:55.860 --> 00:03:57.620
or my rods are harder!

00:03:57.980 --> 00:03:59.100
Yes.

00:04:03.700 --> 00:04:04.700
Father.

00:04:06.980 --> 00:04:08.019
Prince Jing.

00:04:08.020 --> 00:04:11.820
Back then, after your defeat and injury
in battle, you became dispirited.

00:04:11.900 --> 00:04:13.419
I was disappointed in you,

00:04:13.420 --> 00:04:15.380
and that drove a wedge between us.

00:04:15.980 --> 00:04:16.700
I...

00:04:16.820 --> 00:04:18.740
I do not believe those rumors.

00:04:19.100 --> 00:04:20.540
And my son

00:04:20.780 --> 00:04:22.100
is no cursed star.

00:04:24.260 --> 00:04:27.020
Rumors may be silenced,
but people's hearts are hard to change.

00:04:29.300 --> 00:04:32.100
I'm willing to go to the military camp
myself and investigate the truth.

00:04:32.460 --> 00:04:34.340
As long as the problem is solved,

00:04:34.460 --> 00:04:36.620
the rumors
will naturally disappear on their own.

00:04:43.180 --> 00:04:44.540
Mother.

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:46.500
The Imperial Preceptor
truly knows what he's doing.

00:04:46.780 --> 00:04:47.980
Once the grain depot burns

00:04:48.420 --> 00:04:49.579
and the rumors spread,

00:04:49.580 --> 00:04:52.860
Xiao Heng will have no choice but to go.

00:04:53.780 --> 00:04:54.819
Grandmother.

00:04:54.820 --> 00:04:56.179
Father.

00:04:56.180 --> 00:04:58.380
Without grain,

00:04:58.500 --> 00:05:01.300
the soldiers will go hungry.

00:05:01.500 --> 00:05:04.580
If they have nothing to eat...

00:05:04.860 --> 00:05:05.940
What did you say?

00:05:13.560 --> 00:05:16.879
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:05:16.880 --> 00:05:20.719
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:05:20.720 --> 00:05:24.239
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:05:24.240 --> 00:05:27.200
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:05:28.080 --> 00:05:31.719
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:35.480
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:05:35.560 --> 00:05:38.879
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:42.920
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:05:48.520 --> 00:05:52.199
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:05:52.200 --> 00:05:55.839
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:05:55.840 --> 00:05:59.559
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:05:59.560 --> 00:06:03.199
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:06:03.200 --> 00:06:06.879
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:06:06.880 --> 00:06:08.799
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:06:08.800 --> 00:06:15.000
♪Good fortune♪